{"word":"G2920 - κρίσις - krísis - kree'-sis - Accusation","slug":"G2920","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κρίσις</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>krísis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kree'-sis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Accusation"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03B9;&#x03C2; - krisis</b> - <i>kree'-sis</i><p/>(Subjectively or objectively, for or against); by extension a <i>tribunal</i>; by implication <i>justice</i> (specifically divine <i>law</i>): - accusation, condemnation, damnation, judgment."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1252\">G1252</a>, <a href=\"#/G1253\">G1253</a>, <a href=\"#/G1469\">G1469</a>, <a href=\"#/G178\">G178</a>, <a href=\"#/G2631\">G2631</a>, <a href=\"#/G2632\">G2632</a>, <a href=\"#/G2633\">G2633</a>, <a href=\"#/G2917\">G2917</a>, <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>, <a href=\"#/G2922\">G2922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2923\">G2923</a>, <a href=\"#/G2924\">G2924</a>, <a href=\"#/G350\">G350</a>, <a href=\"#/G351\">G351</a>, <a href=\"#/G470\">G470</a>, <a href=\"#/G610\">G610</a>, <a href=\"#/G611\">G611</a>, <a href=\"#/G612\">G612</a>, <a href=\"#/G843\">G843</a>, <a href=\"#/G87\">G87</a>"}]}